query: SELECT MIN(T1.Artwork_ID), T3.Festival_Name FROM nomination AS T1 INNER JOIN festival_detail AS T3 ON T1.Festival_ID = T3.Festival_ID INNER JOIN artwork AS T2 ON T1.Artwork_ID = T2.Artwork_ID WHERE T3.Year BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND T3.Year NOT IN (SELECT Year FROM festival_detail AS n WHERE n.Num_of_Audience BETWEEN 1 AND 10) LIMIT 6
question: What are the next six festival names with the smallest artwork IDs, where the festivals are held in the first ten years but do not have audience numbers between 1 and 10 in those years?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT q.Artwork_ID), q.Festival_ID, q.Result FROM nomination AS q WHERE  q.Artwork_ID > 47 ORDER BY q.Festival_ID ASC LIMIT 4
question: What are the festival ids and results of the distinct artworks with id greater than 47, ordered by festival id in ascending order, from the 5th to the 8th rows?

query: SELECT T1.Max_Artwork_ID, T2.Artwork_ID, T2.Name FROM (SELECT Name, MAX(Artwork_ID) AS Max_Artwork_ID FROM artwork GROUP BY Name) T1 JOIN artwork T2 ON T1.Name = T2.Name AND T1.Max_Artwork_ID = T2.Artwork_ID LIMIT 2
question: What are the names and ids of the two artworks with the highest artwork id for each artwork name, excluding the first one?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.Result) FROM nomination AS c WHERE c.Artwork_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  c.Festival_ID < 21
question: How many distinct results are there for artworks with IDs between 1 and 10, nominated in festivals with IDs less than 21?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT h.Type) FROM artwork AS h WHERE h.Artwork_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  h.Artwork_ID <= 14
question: What is the number of distinct artwork types for artworks with IDs between 1 and 10 or less than or equal to 14?

query: SELECT T3.Num_of_Audience, T2.Result FROM artwork AS T1 JOIN nomination AS T2 ON T1.Artwork_ID = T2.Artwork_ID JOIN festival_detail AS T3 ON T2.Festival_ID = T3.Festival_ID WHERE T3.Festival_ID IN (SELECT Festival_ID FROM festival_detail)
question: What are the results of the artworks and the number of audience in the festivals?

query: SELECT Year, Location FROM festival_detail WHERE  Festival_ID <= 69 ORDER BY Location DESC
question: What are the years and locations of the festivals with an id less than or equal to 69, listed in descending order by location?

query: SELECT Festival_Name FROM festival_detail WHERE Festival_ID IN (SELECT Festival_ID FROM nomination) ORDER BY Festival_Name ASC;
question: What are the names of all the festivals that have had a nomination, listed in alphabetical order?

query: SELECT COUNT(nomination.Artwork_ID), festival_detail.Num_of_Audience FROM artwork JOIN nomination ON artwork.Artwork_ID = nomination.Artwork_ID JOIN festival_detail ON nomination.Festival_ID = festival_detail.Festival_ID WHERE festival_detail.Year != (SELECT MIN(Year) FROM festival_detail AS r WHERE r.Num_of_Audience BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  r.Festival_ID < 82) LIMIT 10
question: What are the counts of artwork nominations and corresponding audience numbers for the 11th to 20th festivals, excluding the earliest festival with an audience between 1 and 10 or a festival ID less than 82?

query: SELECT Chair_Name, Location FROM festival_detail WHERE  Year = 76 AND Num_of_Audience > (SELECT MIN(Num_of_Audience) FROM festival_detail AS k WHERE  k.Num_of_Audience < 48) GROUP BY Chair_Name ORDER BY Location DESC
question: What are the chair names and locations of the 1976 festivals with audience numbers greater than the minimum audience number of any festival with less than 48 attendees, listed in descending order by location?

query: SELECT Artwork_ID FROM nomination WHERE Artwork_ID NOT IN (SELECT Artwork_ID FROM artwork)
question: What are the artwork ids of artworks that are not in the artwork table?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Chair_Name), Location FROM festival_detail ORDER BY Location DESC
question: What is the number of unique chair names and the location of festivals in descending order of location?

query: SELECT Name, Type FROM artwork JOIN nomination ON artwork.Artwork_ID = nomination.Artwork_ID
question: What are the names and types of artworks that have been nominated?

query: SELECT Name FROM artwork WHERE Artwork_ID = 36;
question: What is the name of the artwork with id 36?

query: SELECT SUM(nomination.Festival_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT artwork.Artwork_ID), artwork.Artwork_ID FROM artwork JOIN nomination ON artwork.Artwork_ID = nomination.Artwork_ID WHERE  artwork.Artwork_ID < 87 GROUP BY artwork.Artwork_ID;
question: For artworks with an id less than 87, what is the total festival id and how many artwork ids are there, grouped by each artwork id?

query: SELECT e.Num_of_Audience FROM festival_detail AS e WHERE e.Num_of_Audience BETWEEN 1 AND 10
question: What are the audience numbers of festivals with between 1 and 10 attendees?

query: SELECT Artwork_ID, Type FROM artwork WHERE Artwork_ID < 14 GROUP BY Type ORDER BY Artwork_ID ASC;
question: What are the types of artworks with IDs less than 14, listed in ascending order of artwork ID?

query: SELECT Result, Type FROM nomination JOIN artwork ON nomination.Artwork_ID = artwork.Artwork_ID ORDER BY Type ASC;
question: What are the results and types of artworks in ascending order of type?

query: SELECT T3.Year FROM artwork AS T1 INNER JOIN nomination AS T2 ON T1.Artwork_ID = T2.Artwork_ID INNER JOIN festival_detail AS T3 ON T2.Festival_ID = T3.Festival_ID WHERE T3.Year >= 1974 ORDER BY T3.Year ASC;
question: What are the years of the festivals with at least one artwork nomination, starting from 1974 onwards?

query: SELECT SUM(festival_detail.Festival_ID), MIN(festival_detail.Num_of_Audience), festival_detail.Chair_Name FROM artwork JOIN nomination ON artwork.Artwork_ID = nomination.Artwork_ID JOIN festival_detail ON nomination.Festival_ID = festival_detail.Festival_ID WHERE festival_detail.Year = 2015
question: In 2015, what was the total festival ID, the minimum number of audience, and the chair's name for the festivals where artworks were nominated?

query: SELECT Artwork_ID, COUNT(*) FROM artwork WHERE Artwork_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Artwork_ID >= 16 GROUP BY Artwork_ID;
question: What is the number of artworks for each artwork with an ID between 1 and 10 or 16 and above?

query: SELECT MAX(T2.Num_of_Audience), T1.Artwork_ID, T2.Num_of_Audience FROM artwork AS T1 INNER JOIN nomination AS T3 ON T1.Artwork_ID = T3.Artwork_ID INNER JOIN festival_detail AS T2 ON T3.Festival_ID = T2.Festival_ID WHERE T2.Festival_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY T1.Artwork_ID, T2.Num_of_Audience LIMIT 10;
question: What are the artwork ids and their corresponding audience numbers for the top 10 artworks with the largest audience at festivals 1 to 10?

query: SELECT AVG(Artwork_ID), MAX(Artwork_ID) FROM artwork;
question: What is the average and maximum artwork id?

query: SELECT COUNT(e.Artwork_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT e.Festival_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT e.Result) FROM nomination AS e WHERE e.Artwork_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  e.Festival_ID = 83
question: For the artworks with id between 1 and 10 or the nominations at festival 83, how many total nominations, distinct festivals, and distinct results are there?

query: SELECT b.Artwork_ID, b.Type FROM artwork AS b WHERE  b.Artwork_ID > 99 GROUP BY b.Type ORDER BY b.Artwork_ID DESC
question: What are the artwork types for artworks with an ID greater than 99, listed in descending order of artwork ID and grouped by type?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT nomination.Artwork_ID), Year FROM artwork JOIN nomination JOIN festival_detail ON nomination.Festival_ID = festival_detail.Festival_ID AND artwork.Artwork_ID = nomination.Artwork_ID WHERE artwork.Artwork_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY Year ASC
question: What are the numbers of distinct artworks nominated for each year, in ascending order of year, for artworks with IDs between 1 and 10?

query: SELECT COUNT(artwork.Artwork_ID), artwork.Artwork_ID, artwork.Name FROM artwork JOIN nomination AS n ON artwork.Artwork_ID = n.Artwork_ID WHERE n.Festival_ID > 84 AND artwork.Artwork_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY artwork.Name, artwork.Artwork_ID HAVING MAX(n.Festival_ID) <= 47 LIMIT 2
question: What are the next two artworks, identified by their IDs and names, with the highest count of nominations, that were nominated for festivals with IDs greater than 84, have an artwork ID between 1 and 10, and have their highest festival ID no more than 47?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Location), Festival_ID, Year FROM festival_detail WHERE Num_of_Audience BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Festival_Name > (SELECT MAX(Festival_Name) FROM festival_detail WHERE Festival_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Num_of_Audience < 74)
question: What is the count of distinct locations and the corresponding festival id and year for festivals with audience between 1 and 10 and name greater than the maximum name of festivals with id between 1 and 10 or audience less than 74?

query: SELECT T1.Festival_Name, T3.Result, T1.Festival_Name FROM festival_detail AS T1 INNER JOIN nomination AS T3 ON T1.Festival_ID = T3.Festival_ID INNER JOIN artwork AS T2 ON T2.Artwork_ID = T3.Artwork_ID WHERE T2.Artwork_ID < 76
question: What are the names of festivals and their corresponding results for artworks with an ID less than 76?

query: SELECT MAX(t.Artwork_ID), t.Artwork_ID FROM artwork AS t WHERE  t.Artwork_ID != 60
question: What is the highest artwork id other than 60?

query: SELECT a.Artwork_ID, a.Name FROM artwork AS a WHERE  a.Artwork_ID > 55 LIMIT 9
question: What are the names of the 10th to 18th artworks by artwork ID?

query: SELECT artwork.Artwork_ID FROM artwork JOIN nomination ON artwork.Artwork_ID = nomination.Artwork_ID WHERE artwork.Artwork_ID <= 23 ORDER BY artwork.Artwork_ID ASC
question: What are the artwork IDs less than or equal to 23 that have been nominated, listed in ascending order?

query: SELECT Location, Chair_Name FROM festival_detail WHERE Festival_ID NOT IN (SELECT Festival_ID FROM nomination) ORDER BY Chair_Name DESC;
question: What are the locations and chair names of the festivals without any nominations, listed in descending order by chair name?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n.Festival_ID), n.Festival_ID FROM nomination n JOIN festival_detail f ON n.Festival_ID = f.Festival_ID WHERE f.Festival_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR f.Num_of_Audience >= (SELECT AVG(Num_of_Audience) FROM festival_detail) GROUP BY n.Festival_ID HAVING COUNT(n.Festival_ID) = 1 ORDER BY n.Festival_ID ASC LIMIT 9
question: What are the next 9 festival IDs with only one nomination that either have a festival ID between 1 and 10, or have a number of audience greater than or equal to the average number of audience across all festivals?
